34
00:03:08,610 --> 00:03:10,830
I've got a real job now, y'know!

35
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:12,420
Huh? You've got a job?

36
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:17,270
Yes, Master Koichi! I found myself a
little job that involves financing.

37
00:03:17,270 --> 00:03:18,840
Financing?

38
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:21,830
You don't mean you became a loan shark, do you?

39
00:03:21,830 --> 00:03:25,270
Well... It's a very reputable
establishment, though!

40
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:30,390
Still, though, we can't just ignore this.

41
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:33,500
Wait up, Josuke!

42
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,600
M-Master Koichi!

43
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,330
Are you going, too?

44
00:03:37,330 --> 00:03:39,830
Just leave it to that idiot Josuke.

45
00:03:40,330 --> 00:03:43,800
There's something scary going on in my town.

46
00:03:44,450 --> 00:03:48,230
If Morioh City is in danger,
that means my parents, my sister,

47
00:03:48,230 --> 00:03:51,660
and everyone else important to me
will have to face that danger.

48
00:03:52,090 --> 00:03:54,290
So even if it's scary, I gotta do something!

49
00:03:56,140 --> 00:03:56,970
Wh...

50
00:03:57,550 --> 00:03:59,660
What a tough thing to say.

51
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:02,450
Nothing less from the man I've chosen to admire!

52
00:04:03,610 --> 00:04:04,490
But...

53
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:08,550
