57
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:28,630
But if that Hazamada guy really
did gouge out his friend's eye

58
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:31,790
and can still blend into normal school life...

59
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:36,670
He must be one creepy guy.

60
00:04:42,590 --> 00:04:43,720
Hazamada

61
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:46,340
H-Hey, Josuke!

62
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:51,000
