64
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,810
For starters... His bag is still here.

65
00:04:57,340 --> 00:05:00,100
So he's still at school. Be careful.

66
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:01,320
R-Right.

67
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:06,480
So he's in the tennis club and likes manga.

68
00:05:08,130 --> 00:05:10,750
Still, this guy's got way too much stuff.

69
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:14,640
