226
00:13:52,530 --> 00:13:53,670
Josuke...

227
00:13:54,650 --> 00:13:56,380
Hey, read this.

228
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,980
B-Bye.

229
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:04,440
